dynamicalSystems
Class IfThenElse

java.lang.Object
  dynamicalSystems.Entity
      dynamicalSystems.IfThenElse

public class IfThenElse
extends Entity

An IfThenElse object is formed by a Condition,and Two possible solution.

condition is the Condition to be evaluated.

solutionCaseTrue is the first Entity. If the condition is true,the ifThenElse result, is the solutionCaseTrue's value.

solutionCaseFalse is the second Entity.If the condition is false, the ifThenElse result, is the solutionCaseFalse's value.

Author:
Wellington Bruno
